headline: Enovix Establishes R&D Center of Excellence in India to Accelerate AI-2™ Platform Development
summary: FREMONT, Calif., Aug. 08, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Enovix Corporation (Nasdaq: ENVX) (“Company” or “Enovix”), a global high-performance battery company, today announced that it has created an R&D Center of Excellence in Hyderabad, India to accelerate the development of its Artificial Intelligence ClassTM second-generation battery platform AI-2TM into 2025.
